        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Choose between highlighting with inline CSS or CSS classes. Please note that there are pros and cons to both choices. Inline CSS will keep you from being reliant on external CSS files if you choose to export your notes. CSS classes are more flexible and easier to customize.",
          "target": "选择使用内联 CSS 还是 CSS 类进行高亮。请注意，两种选择各有利弊。如果您选择导出笔记，内联 CSS 将使您无需依赖外部 CSS 文件。CSS 类更灵活，也更容易自定义。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "The \"Painter: Clear\" command clears all \"mark\" elements. However, you might wish to remove other elements as well. Add CSS Selectors to be cleaned here (one per line)",
          "target": "“Painter: Clear” 命令会清除所有 “mark” 元素。但是，您可能还希望移除其他元素。在此处添加要清理的 CSS 选择器（每行一个）"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Normally, new highlights overwrite old ones. Turn this off to keep previous highlights when highlighting. You will have to clear highlights manually when changing their color.",
          "target": "通常，新的高亮会覆盖旧的高亮。关闭此选项可在高亮时保留之前的高亮。更改高亮颜色时，您需要手动清除高亮。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Depending on your design aesthetic, you may want to customize the style of your highlights. Choose from an assortment of different highlighter styles by using the dropdown. Depending on your theme, this plugin's CSS may be overriden.",
          "target": "根据您的设计美学，您可能希望自定义高亮的样式。使用下拉菜单从各种不同的荧光笔样式中进行选择。根据您的主题，此插件的 CSS 可能会被覆盖。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Create new highlight colors by providing a color name and using the color picker to set the hex code value. Don't forget to save the color before exiting the color picker. Drag and drop the highlight color to change the order for your highlighter component.",
